 effects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/194133/', '', 'Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Trimethobenzamide, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', '', 1767369485);
